{"id":67,"parent_id":64,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":67,"title":"Jacob 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jacob","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","The pure in heart receive the pleasing word of God—Lamanite righteousness exceeds that of the Nephites—Jacob warns against fornication, lasciviousness, and every sin. About 544–421",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.1","order":"05.14.003.7267"},["b","1"],"But behold, I, Jacob, would speak unto you that are pure in heart. Look unto God with firmness of mind, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"pray"],"unto him with exceeding faith, and he will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"console"],"you in your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"afflictions"],", and he will plead your cause, and send down",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"justice"],"upon those who seek your destruction."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.2","order":"05.14.003.7268"},["b","2"],"O all ye that are pure in heart, lift up your heads and receive the pleasing word of God, and feast upon his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"love"],"; for ye may, if your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"minds"],"are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"firm"],", forever."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.3","order":"05.14.003.7269"},["b","3"],"But, wo, wo, unto you that are not pure in heart, that are filthy this day before God; for except ye repent the land is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"cursed"],"for your sakes; and the Lamanites, which are not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"filthy"],"like unto you, nevertheless they are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"cursed"],"with a sore cursing, shall scourge you even unto destruction."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.4","order":"05.14.003.7270"},["b","4"],"And the time speedily cometh, that except ye repent they shall possess the land of your inheritance, and the Lord God will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"lead"],"away the righteous out from among you."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.5","order":"05.14.003.7271"},["b","5"],"Behold, the Lamanites your brethren, whom ye hate because of their filthiness and the cursing which hath come upon their skins, are more righteous than you; for they have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"forgotten"],"the commandment of the Lord, which was given unto our father—that they should have save it were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"one"],"wife, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"concubines"],"they should have none, and there should not be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"whoredoms"],"committed among them."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.6","order":"05.14.003.7272"},["b","6"],"And now, this commandment they observe to keep; wherefore, because of this observance, in keeping this commandment, the Lord God will not destroy them, but will be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"merciful"],"unto them; and one day they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"become"],"a blessed people."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.7","order":"05.14.003.7273"},["b","7"],"Behold, their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"husbands"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"love"],"their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"wives"],", and their wives love their husbands; and their husbands and their wives love their children; and their",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"unbelief"],"and their hatred towards you is because of the iniquity of their fathers; wherefore, how much better are you than they, in the sight of your great Creator?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.8","order":"05.14.003.7274"},["b","8"],"O my brethren, I fear that unless ye shall repent of your sins that their skins will be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"whiter"],"than yours, when ye shall be brought with them before the throne of God."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.9","order":"05.14.003.7275"},["b","9"],"Wherefore, a commandment I give unto you, which is the word of God, that ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"revile"],"no more against them because of the darkness of their skins; neither shall ye revile against them because of their filthiness; but ye shall remember your own filthiness, and remember that their filthiness came because of their fathers."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.10","order":"05.14.003.7276"},["b","10"],"Wherefore, ye shall remember your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"children"],", how that ye have grieved their hearts because of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"example"],"that ye have set before them; and also, remember that ye may, because of your filthiness, bring your children unto destruction, and their sins be heaped upon your heads at the last day."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.11","order":"05.14.003.7277"},["b","11"],"O my brethren, hearken unto my words;",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"arouse"],"the faculties of your souls; shake yourselves that ye may",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"awake"],"from the slumber of death; and loose yourselves from the pains of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"hell"],"that ye may not become",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"angels"],"to the devil, to be cast into that lake of fire and brimstone which is the second",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_11e"},"death"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.12","order":"05.14.003.7278"},["b","12"],"And now I, Jacob, spake many more things unto the people of Nephi,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"warning"],"them against",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"fornication"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"lasciviousness"],", and every kind of sin, telling them the awful consequences of them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.13","order":"05.14.003.7279"},["b","13"],"And a hundredth part of the proceedings of this people, which now began to be numerous, cannot be written upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"these plates"],"; but many of their proceedings are written upon the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"larger plates"],", and their wars, and their contentions, and the reigns of their kings."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.14","order":"05.14.003.7280"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"These"],"plates are called the plates of Jacob, and they were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"made"],"by the hand of Nephi. And I make an end of speaking these words."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.1a","order":"05.14.003.7281"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32.8"},"2 Ne. 32:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.1b","order":"05.14.003.7283"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/comfort"},"TG Comfort"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/consolation"},"Consolation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"Purity"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.1c","order":"05.14.003.7285"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/affliction"},"TG Affliction"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.1d","order":"05.14.003.7287"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.2a","order":"05.14.003.7289"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"TG God, Love of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.2b","order":"05.14.003.7291"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/steadfastness"},"TG Steadfastness"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.2c","order":"05.14.003.7293"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/57.27"},"Alma 57:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.3a","order":"05.14.003.7295"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-curse-of"},"TG Earth, Curse of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.3b","order":"05.14.003.7297"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/filthiness"},"TG Filthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.3c","order":"05.14.003.7299"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/12.23"},"1 Ne. 12:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.4a","order":"05.14.003.7301"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/omni/1.12.5-7,12-13"},"Omni 1:12 (5–7, 12–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.5a","order":"05.14.003.7303"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.35"},"Jacob 2:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.5b","order":"05.14.003.7305"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.27"},"Jacob 2:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.5c","order":"05.14.003.7307"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.2.2-14"},"Mosiah 11:2 (2–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/10.5"},"Ether 10:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.5d","order":"05.14.003.7309"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastity"},"TG Chastity"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.6a","order":"05.14.003.7311"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.31"},"1 Ne. 13:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.7"},"2 Ne. 4:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.18.18-19"},"10:18 (18–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/15.12.10-17"},"Hel. 15:12 (10–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.20.20-21"},"Morm. 5:20 (20–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.6b","order":"05.14.003.7313"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/15.14.13-18"},"1 Ne. 15:14 (13–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.8"},"22:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.7a","order":"05.14.003.7315"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-husbands"},"TG Marriage, Husbands"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.7b","order":"05.14.003.7317"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"TG Family, Love within"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-continuing-courtship-in"},"Marriage, Continuing Courtship in"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.7c","order":"05.14.003.7319"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-wives"},"TG Marriage, Wives"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.7d","order":"05.14.003.7321"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.18"},"D&C 3:18"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"TG Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.8a","order":"05.14.003.7323"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/2.15"},"3 Ne. 2:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.9a","order":"05.14.003.7325"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reviling"},"TG Reviling"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.10a","order":"05.14.003.7327"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-responsibilities-toward"},"TG Family, Children, Responsibilities toward"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"Family, Love within"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.10b","order":"05.14.003.7329"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/exa